---
title: Crispy Fried Chicken Bites & Gravy with Mashed Potatoes & Creamy Coleslaw
description: This hearty, satisfying meal is packed with classic Southern flavors—the definition of comfort food. You'll whip up crispy fried chicken bites, buttery mashed potatoes swirled with sour cream, and creamy gravy that ties each bite together. A side of crunchy, refreshing coleslaw completes the feast!
